OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776767959
OL,3,CNew bowel cancer treatment 'highly
OL,4,Ceffective', research suggests
OL,6,FTreating some bowel cancer patients
OL,7,Fwith immunotherapy before surgery
OL,8,Fimproves survival and cuts the need
OL,9,Ffor chemotherapy, according to new
OL,10,Fresearch.
OL,12,FA study found zero relapses among
OL,13,Fpatients given a new treatment regime,
OL,14,Fwith far better results than would
OL,15,Fotherwise be expected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
