PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776767959
OL,3,CNew bowel cancer treatment 'highly
OL,4,Ceffective', research suggests
OL,6,FThe work builds on earlier results
OL,7,Fshowing that nine weeks of pre-
OL,8,Foperative immunotherapy using the drug
OL,9,Fpembrolizumab led to major tumour
OL,10,Fshrinkage in patients with stage two
OL,11,For three bowel cancer.
OL,13,FSome 59% of patients had no signs of
OL,14,Fdisease after having pembrolizumab and
OL,15,Fthen their planned bowel cancer
OL,16,Foperation.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
