OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776767959
OL,3,CNew bowel cancer treatment 'highly
OL,4,Ceffective', research suggests
OL,6,FThe trial was led by University
OL,7,FCollege London (UCL) and University
OL,8,FCollege London Hospitals NHS
OL,9,FFoundation Trust (UCLH), with experts
OL,10,Fpresenting their findings at the
OL,11,FAmerican Association for Cancer
OL,12,FResearch (AACR) meeting in San Diego,
OL,13,FCalifornia.
OL,15,FThe NEOPRISM-CRC trial involved 32
OL,16,Fpatients recruited with stage two or
OL,17,Fthree bowel cancer and a certain
OL,18,Fgenetic profile (MMR deficient/MSI-
OL,19,Fhigh bowel cancer) from five hospitals
OL,20,Faround the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
