FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776767959
OL,3,CNew bowel cancer treatment 'highly
OL,4,Ceffective', research suggests
OL,6,FAround 10-15% of patients with stage
OL,7,Ftwo or three bowel cancer have this
OL,8,Fgenetic profile, making up around
OL,9,F2,000-3,000 bowel cancer cases per
OL,10,Fyear in the UK.
OL,12,FWhile the study looked at this
OL,13,Fspecific group of patients,
OL,14,Fresearchers are hopeful their approach
OL,15,Fcan be extended to others with bowel
OL,16,Fcancer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
