OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776767959
OL,3,CNew bowel cancer treatment 'highly
OL,4,Ceffective', research suggests
OL,6,FDr Kai-Keen Shiu, chief investigator
OL,7,Ffrom the UCL Cancer Institute and a
OL,8,Fconsultant medical oncologist at UCLH,
OL,9,Fsaid the results were "extremely
OL,10,Fencouraging" and that they strengthen
OL,11,Fconfidence that pembrolizumab is "a
OL,12,Fsafe and highly effective treatment"
OL,13,Fto improve outcomes in patients with
OL,14,Fhigh-risk bowel cancers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
