PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776767959
OL,3,CNew bowel cancer treatment 'highly
OL,4,Ceffective', research suggests
OL,6,F"What is particularly exciting is that
OL,7,Fwe now may be able to predict who will
OL,8,Frespond to the treatment using
OL,9,Fpersonalised blood tests and immune
OL,10,Fprofiling," she added, saying this
OL,11,Fwould help medics to tailor patients'
OL,12,Ftreatment better.
OL,14,FPatients were given up to nine weeks
OL,15,Fof pembrolizumab prior to bowel
OL,16,Fsurgery, instead of the usual
OL,17,Ftreatment of surgery followed by three
OL,18,Fto six months of chemotherapy, then
OL,19,Fmonitored over time.
