PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776767959
OL,3,CNew bowel cancer treatment 'highly
OL,4,Ceffective', research suggests
OL,6,F"The recovery went fine," he said. "I
OL,7,Fdidn't have any problems. And since
OL,8,Fthen, I've been feeling pretty much
OL,9,Fback to normal.
OL,11,F"I feel very lucky that I've reached
OL,12,Fthe stage where my main problem is age
OL,13,Frather than cancer or any illness.
OL,15,F"I am able to play guitar, tend my
OL,16,Fgarden and walk the dog very much as
OL,17,Fbefore and I look forward to spending
OL,18,Ftime with friends and family."
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@YO]nD@dOUsD@AOUwD@AOUzD@^O]
